    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The e2e test seems to actually catch a bug; if a refinement is set again to the default value of the widget (usually nothing) the previous value for uiState is kept by the widget. This is expected on first render, but not later.",
    "created_at": "2020-05-05T09:41:04Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/pull/4359#issuecomment-623956641",
    "id": 623956641,
    "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/algolia/instantsearch/issues/4359",
